title: Arrived
description: Seventeen year old Angie is beyond ecstatic for her eighteenth birthday with the promise of getting a car for her special day. Unbeknownst to her, life as she knew it would quickly change with the arrival of the unidentified ships floating in the air.What are they? Who are they? What do they want?Will she get answers to her questions before time runs out?
author: Kathy Dinisi
